defaultal Social Enterprise Programme
default. The aim of this DfT-
defaultsupport
defaulted project was to help 
defaultrural C
defaultommunity 
defaultT
defaultransport operators adopt a more enterprise-led approach, win more contracts and generate more income. Sinc
defaulte leaving BECT I have undertaken some consultancy work for the Community Transport Association
default. I am a parish councillor 
defaultand an elected Parish 
defaultM
defaultember on the Peak District National Park Authority. I also write walking guidebooks and run a website promoting 
defaultcycling in the Peak District. The following submission is from mysel
